<h4 id="terminology">Terminology</h4>
<p>It is the study of geometric properties that are invariant with
respect to projective transformations.</p>

<h4 id="terminology-1">Terminology</h4>
<ol>
  <li>projective line: space of 1-dim subspaces in 2-dim space.</li>
  <li>projective plane: 1-dim subspaces in 3-dim space.</li>
</ol>

<p><img src="/images/space-projective-geometry-cone.png" /></p>

<h4 id="application">application</h4>
